    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "913482_21_3783-3821",
      "chapterUid": 21,
      "range": "3783-3821",
      "markText": "谁能驾驭武人，谁反被武人牵着走？这是时局变动之际，居于领袖地位的人的试金石。",
      "totalCount": 476,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=913482&chapterUid=21&rangeStart=3783&rangeEnd=3821",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/eae327905df04aeaefac8cc?chapterUid=21&rangeStart=3783&rangeEnd=3821"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "913482_12_1301-1383",
      "chapterUid": 12,
      "range": "1301-1383",
      "markText": "然则曹操的所以不可与争锋，还是拥百万之众的关系大，挟天子以令诸侯的关系小。曹操所以能有相当的成功，还是因其政治清明，善于用兵，和挟天子以令诸侯，根本没有多大的关系。",
      "totalCount": 468,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=913482&chapterUid=12&rangeStart=1301&rangeEnd=1383",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/eae327905df04aeaefac8cc?chapterUid=12&rangeStart=1301&rangeEnd=1383"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "913482_16_5516-5560",
      "chapterUid": 16,
      "range": "5516-5560",
      "markText": "天下惟心地光明的人，说话能够坦白。遮遮掩掩，修饰得自己一无弊病的人，他的话就不可尽信了。",
      "totalCount": 432,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=913482&chapterUid=16&rangeStart=5516&rangeEnd=5560",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/eae327905df04aeaefac8cc?chapterUid=16&rangeStart=5516&rangeEnd=5560"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "913482_13_4889-4927",
      "chapterUid": 13,
      "range": "4889-4927",
      "markText": "军事的胜败，固然决于最后五分钟，也要能够支持到最后五分钟，才有决胜的资格哩。",
      "totalCount": 405,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=913482&chapterUid=13&rangeStart=4889&rangeEnd=4927",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/eae327905df04aeaefac8cc?chapterUid=13&rangeStart=4889&rangeEnd=4927"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "913482_4_1498-1531",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "1498-1531",
      "markText": "史事哪有真相同的？我们所谓相同，都不过察之不精，误以不同为同罢了。",
      "totalCount": 348,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=913482&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=1498&rangeEnd=1531",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/eae327905df04aeaefac8cc?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=1498&rangeEnd=1531"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "913482_5_3217-3253",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "3217-3253",
      "markText": "在古代，必须用兵器伤害人的身体，使之成为不能恢复的创伤，然后可以谓之刑。",
      "totalCount": 297,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=913482&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=3217&rangeEnd=3253",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/eae327905df04aeaefac8cc?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=3217&rangeEnd=3253"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "913482_13_5298-5327",
      "chapterUid": 13,
      "range": "5298-5327",
      "markText": "所以说历史上的话，总是不可尽信，我们读书非自出手眼不可的。",
      "totalCount": 272,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=913482&chapterUid=13&rangeStart=5298&rangeEnd=5327",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/eae327905df04aeaefac8cc?chapterUid=13&rangeStart=5298&rangeEnd=5327"
    },
    {
